targets.query:
from(bucket: "mavlink")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "GLOBAL_POSITION_INT" and
    r._field == "alt"
  )
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({ r with _value: r._value * 0.00328084}))
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 500ms, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "mavlink")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "GLOBAL_POSITION_INT" and
    r._field == "hdg"
  )
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({ r with _value: r._value / 100.0 }))
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 500ms, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "mavlink")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "GLOBAL_POSITION_INT" and
    r._field == "hdg"
  )
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({ r with _value: r._value / 100.0 }))
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 500ms, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "mavlink")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["ID"] == "74")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["ID"] == "74")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "groundspeed" or r["_field"] == "airspeed")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")

import "math"

from(bucket: "mavlink")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "ATTITUDE" and
    r._field == "roll"
  )
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({ r with _value: r._value * 180.0 / math.pi }))
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 500ms, fn: mean)
